---

<section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-black via-gray-900 to-black py-10 min-h-screen">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-10">üèÜ Torneos Activos</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
